data.description: Come check out this beautiful move-in ready home just minutes from Jackson Lake where you can enjoy fishing and boating with friends and family! This home has a wonderful open living area, spacious eat in kitchen and great sized bedrooms. The home has a newly installed HVAC and water heater, fresh paint throughout, new LVP flooring in the master bedroom and kitchen, and a newly fenced, large back yard. Also enjoy the new recessed lighting, providing a well-lit workspace for your culinary adventures. There is a pull-down attic for your convenience. The roof is under 2 years old! In case that's not enough, you can use the spacious crawl space, or the backyard shed to store additional items. Don't like the pressure of HOAs? No worries! This community doesn't have one. To make things even more convenient, the seller is offering concessions. ***USDA Eligible -$0 Down!!!
